{"tid":2431773,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"查比高恩斯空難生還者再死過翻生","createTime":"2021-03-04T01:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T01:33:48.000Z","uid":78243,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ad995cfa772d8ec09c2baa1a28ae769cde429c","tid":2431773,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:23:41.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】巴西球隊查比高恩斯空難中一名生還的機組人員，周二在21人死亡的車禍中再次逃出死門關。<br />\n巴西球隊查比高恩斯於2016年的空難中有71人喪生，其中一名生還的機組人員圖米利（Erwin Tumiri），周二在玻利維亞城市高查邦巴山區的遭遇奪命車禍，大巴滾落山坡導致21人死亡，幸好圖米利再次保住性命。<br />\n<br />\n30歲的圖米利說：「我當時邊聽手機邊昏昏欲睡，忽然聽到車廂一陣尖叫，我馬上捉緊扶手、緊挨車廂，以免翻車時摔倒。車子一路在滾，沒有握緊扶手的就像活在洗衣機中一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n他最後被救出送院，膝蓋和背部受傷，姐姐盧絲亞說：「謝天謝地，他再次逃出生天！我跟他通過電話，他說並無大礙。」"},{"pid":"17fea9e2f8bf7aa0c69a12a26d10b8611a6c8b93","tid":2431773,"uid":78243,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:23:55.000Z","msg":"應該話佢好彩定唔好彩"},{"pid":"f5bea63ecec38488990ce9898ec8bb4d3da176b8","tid":2431773,"uid":166262,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:25:04.000Z","msg":"不死刧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f220d439f18b47b36a1cfa2235ff2856b68a3b","tid":2431773,"uid":78243,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"f5bea63ecec38488990ce9898ec8bb4d3da176b8","tid":2431773,"uid":166262,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:25:04.000Z","msg":"不死刧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"兩次都係大部份人死哂﹐佢幸運生還<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5262de971d35f3f28f75d5ed532c3331ca83fe17","tid":2431773,"uid":147367,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:27:19.000Z","msg":"主角威能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8063a9bbce37c57dbd4e2890ccae539c46fa42","tid":2431773,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f5bea63ecec38488990ce9898e